# 6) Margins & margin-left for images

```css
img {
  display: block;        /* makes margin-left affect horizontal placement */
  margin-left: 10%;      /* percent is relative to containing block's width */
  margin: 10px 5% 20px;  /* top right bottom (left omitted -> equals right) */
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}
```

**Important**:

* `margin-left: x%` calculates `%` relative to **width of containing block**.
* If `img` is `display: inline`, horizontal margins may not behave as expected — use `display: block` or `display: inline-block`.

