# 10) Useful CSS shorthand & tips

* **Shorthand margin/padding**:
  `margin: top right bottom left;` (1 value = all sides; 2 = top/bottom right/left; 3 = top right/left bottom; 4 = t r b l)
* **Border shorthand**: `border: 1px solid #000;`
* **Font shorthand**: `font: italic small-caps bold 16px/1.5 "Helvetica", sans-serif;`
* **Transition**: `transition: all 0.2s ease;` (for animations)
* **Flexbox**:

  ```css
  .row { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
  ```
* **Grid**:

  ```css
  .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr; gap: 10px; }
  ```

